reviewText: Excellent good quality, viewed by High resolution DataProjector, reflected picture about 1x2meter. Colours excellent. No artifacts. 100% experiance.

This was beyond our expectations. It is wonderful to see a story Swiss story actually taking place in Switzerland and not in some neighbouring country. Not denigrating those countries, but it is great to see the real places with the real mountains etc. And then the language adds to it's authenticity. Well done!
